    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/a017b63d748b8000b8022009b461e9bd.poster.avif?t=1726135807\" width=314 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/a017b63d748b8000b8022009b461e9bd.webm?t=1726135807\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/a017b63d748b8000b8022009b461e9bd.mp4?t=1726135807\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这是一款通过选择模拟的人生体验的一款人生模拟器<br>你将在开局分配你的潜力到不同的属性来开始你的人生体验<br>在其中你将通过你的智力，财富，颜值，体魄的判定决定你会体验到的事件<br>事件将为你带来不同的独立特质，特质将作为你的人生的钥匙展开后续特殊事件的发生<br>最后你将在一次次事件活到人生的最后，最后将进行你的人生结算获得你的积分<br>在后面使用积分购买特殊特质来解锁进行新的体验与潜力<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你究竟想要活出怎样的人生，是出生懵懂只懂啼哭的婴儿</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/d9accca07a8e34164c13173972552277.gif?t=1726135807\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/d9accca07a8e34164c13173972552277.poster.avif?t=1726135807\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>是那遥远模糊只知玩耍只剩回忆的青雉童年<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/38a29c3b2d0baec1717fa344fd1d3ef1.gif?t=1726135807\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/38a29c3b2d0baec1717fa344fd1d3ef1.poster.avif?t=1726135807\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br>是那拼尽汗水奋笔疾书的百日努力奋斗青春<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171810/extras/e814e4a1deebc913005d891e80576cb5.poster.avif?t=1726135807\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.ste